description: List major or minor versions of an environment template with detail data.

parameters.name: majorVersion
parameters.description: To view a list of minor of versions under a major version of an environment template, include major Version. To view a list of major versions of an environment template, exclude major Version.

parameters.name: templateName
parameters.description: The name of the environment template.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates the location of the next major or minor version in the array of major or minor versions of an environment template, after the list of major or minor versions that was previously requested.

nested_items.name: templateVersions
nested_items.description: An array of major or minor versions of an environment template detail data.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the version of an environment template.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time when the version of an environment template was created.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A description of the version of an environment template.

nested_items.name: lastModifiedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the version of an environment template was last modified.

nested_items.name: majorVersion
nested_items.description: The latest major version that's associated with the version of an environment template.

nested_items.name: minorVersion
nested_items.description: The version of an environment template.

nested_items.name: recommendedMinorVersion
nested_items.description: The recommended minor version of the environment template.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the version of an environment template.

nested_items.name: statusMessage
nested_items.description: The status message of the version of an environment template.

nested_items.name: templateName
nested_items.description: The name of the environment template.
